    "description": "<p>Fortune 9 is in the business of:<br>\n1. We have our self-branded beverages, that incorporates proprietary swiss tech (Powder format). Our product features a patented 2-chamber system delivery.<br>\n2. We wholly own the brand, and we are the sole brand principle for our line of beverages<br>\n3. We work with contract packers, to produce our products exclusively<br>\n4. We work with Distributors, and direct key accounts in Singapore, to wholesale and retail our self-branded beverages<br>\n5. We work with Distributors world-wide, to exclusively distribute our products<br>\n6. We perform R&amp;D in-house<br>\nFortune 9 owns the beverage brand No.9. No.9 is a revolutionary 3rd generation beverage, that incorporates Swiss Science in a 2 chamber delivery system, paired with 100% coconut water.<br>\n</p>",
